http://<your-ip>:30007
🧩 STEP 9: CI/CD Flow (Understand for Viva)
🔁 CI (Continuous Integration)
Code pushed to GitHub
Jenkins pulls code automatically
🚀 CD (Continuous Deployment)
Docker builds image
Kubernetes deploys app
